  <VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;[dataDiscovery] revealed the location of a [adj] underground [structureType] where [inventor_nameFull] rests in cryptosleep. The journey will be grueling, as the site is afflicted by a[coldSnapDesc], bringing the region into unnaturally low temperatures. \n\nInside the bunker, a few [turretDefense] still guard the interior, powered by an ancient [arcName]. The ARC cannot be studied but can be deconstructed for [arcComponents]. Your primary task, however, is to reach the casket and release the inventor. Prepare carefully for the extreme cold or risk severe [hypothermiaDanger].</VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription-&gt;Recovered data points us to a [adj] bunker buried deep beneath a region suffering from a[coldSnapDesc]. It is here that [inventor_nameFull], the legendary mind behind the ARC project, lies sealed in cryptosleep. \n\nThe area’s temperatures are falling to dangerous lows, creating an immediate risk of [hypothermiaDanger] during your approach. Inside, [turretDefense] remain active, powered by an overgrown [arcName]. The ARC can be deconstructed for [arcComponents], but the real prize is freeing the inventor and bringing them back to your colony.</VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
