  <VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>questDescription-&gt;We’ve identified the location of a [adj] [structureType] where [inventor_nameFull] has been preserved in a cryptosleep casket. The area surrounding the site is cursed with a[coldSnapDesc], plummeting temperatures to deadly extremes. \n\nThe bunker itself houses a few [turretDefense], powered by an overgrown [arcName]. While the ARC cannot be studied, it can be salvaged for [arcComponents]. Be ready for freezing conditions and hypothermia as you attempt to retrieve the legendary inventor.</VQE_InventorShelter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
